        .balloon:nth-child(2) { background-color: rgba(135, 206, 250, 0.7); left: 10%; animation-duration: 18s; animation-delay: 2s; transform: scale(0.8); }
        .balloon:nth-child(3) { background-color: rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.7); left: 30%; animation-duration: 12s; animation-delay: 4s; transform: scale(1.1); }
        .balloon:nth-child(4) { background-color: rgba(147, 112, 219, 0.7); left: 50%; animation-duration: 20s; animation-delay: 0s; transform: scale(0.9); }
        .balloon:nth-child(5) { background-color: rgba(60, 179, 113, 0.7); left: 70%; animation-duration: 16s; animation-delay: 3s; transform: scale(1.2); }

        .balloon:nth-child(7) { background-color: rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.7); left: 5%; animation-duration: 17s; animation-delay: 5s; transform: scale(1.0); }

        @keyframes floatBalloon {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) scale(var(--scale, 1)) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0.7; }

        }

        /* --- Lock Screen Styling --- */

        /* NEW UNLOCK BUTTON STYLE */
        .unlock-btn {

        }

        }

        /* --- Surprise Content Styling --- */

        /* --- 2. Special Letter Design --- */

        }
        
        /* Typewriter Cursor */
        #typewriterText {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555; 
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            min-height: 150px;
            border-right: 2px solid #ff3366; 
            animation: blink-caret .75s step-end infinite;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;

        }

        #cheesyLinesOutput {

            padding-right: 5px;
            min-height: 100px; 
        }
        
        @keyframes blink-caret { from, to { border-color: transparent } 50% { border-color: #ff3366; } }
        
        /* Hide the blinking cursor when the typing is done */
        .typing-done #cheesyLinesOutput, .typing-done #typewriterText {
             border-color: transparent;
             animation: none;
        }

        /* --- 4. Photo Grid Styling (UPDATED) --- */
        .photo-grid {

        }

        .photo-item {

        }

        .photo-item:hover {

        }

        .photo-item img {

        }

        .photo-item p {
            padding: 15px 10px;

            display: flex;

        }

        /* --- 5. Cheesy Lines Section Styling --- */
        #step5 .cheesy-container {

        }

        /* --- Footer --- */
        footer {

        <div class="balloon" style="--scale: 1.2;"></div>
        <div class="balloon" style="--scale: 0.7;"></div>
        <div class="balloon" style="--scale: 1.0;"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="lockScreen" class="lock-screen">
        <span class="padlock-icon">üîí</span>
        
        <h2>Enter The Secret Key</h2>
        <p>Only the recipient holds the key to the surprise...</p>
        
        <div class="input-group">
            <input type="password" id="secretCode" placeholder="Secret Code" maxlength="10"> 
            <button class="unlock-btn" onclick="checkCode()">Unlock Surprise ‚ú®</button> 
        </div>
        
        <p id="errorMsg" class="error-msg"></p>
    </div>
    <div id="surpriseContent" class="hidden">
        
        <section id="step1" class="surprise-step">
            <h1>‚ú® Happy Birthday, Jaan! ‚ú®</h1>
            <p>Welcome to your special website, designed with all my love.</p>
            <button class="next-btn" onclick="showNextStep(2)">Next Surprise: A Special Letter üíå</button>
        </section>

        <section id="step2" class="surprise-step message-section">
            <h2 class="letter-title">A Special Letter</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--secondary-pink); margin-top: -10px;">Just for you, on your special day üíñ</p>
            
            <div class="letter-card" id="letterCard">
                <span class="corner-heart top-left">‚≠ê</span>

        <section id="step4" class="surprise-step">
            <h2>üì∏ Our Golden Memories (With Her) üì∏</h2>
            <div class="photo-grid">
                <div class="photo-item"><img src=" data:image/jpeg;base64, " alt="Memory 1"><p>The day we first met ‚ù§Ô∏è</p></div>

                <div class="photo-item"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Memory 3"><p>Silly moments are the best!</p></div>
                <div class="photo-item"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Memory 4"><p>Love moments are the best!</p></div>
                            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.5em; color: var(--primary-pink); font-weight: 600;">Happy Birthday once again! I love you!</p>
            
            <button class="next-btn" onclick="showNextStep(5)">Beautiful Lines For You: ‡§ú‡§æ‡§®‡•á ‡§ï‡•á ‡§≤‡§ø‡§è ‡§ï‡•ç‡§≤‡§ø‡§ï ‡§ï‡§∞‡•á‡§Ç üëâ</button>

        </section>

        <section id="step5" class="surprise-step">
            <h2>üíñ Beautiful Lines Just For You üíñ</h2>
            <p style="color: #ccc; margin-top: -10px;">(Box ‡§™‡§∞ Tap ‡§ï‡§∞‡•á‡§Ç)</p>
            <div class="cheesy-container" onclick="typeNextCheesyLine()">
                <div id="cheesyLinesOutput"></div>
                <span id="tapToSeeNext"></span>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.5em; color: var(--primary-pink); font-weight: 600;">Always remember how much I adore you!</p>
            
            <button class="back-to-start-btn" onclick="backToLockScreen()">üö™ Start Screen ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∏ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§è‡§Å</button>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>Made with endless love by your boyfriend, <span style="color: yellow; font-weight: bold;">Piyush</span>.</p>

    <script>
        // --- JAVASCRIPT LOGIC ---
        const SECRET_CODE = "HAPPYB"; 
        const typeSpeed = 70; 
        const CHEESY_TYPE_SPEED = 50;
        
        // --- Cheesy Lines Data ---
        const CHEESY_LINES = [
            "Are you a magician? Because whenever I look at you, everyone else disappears.",
            "Excuse me, but I think you dropped something... My jaw.",
            "I must be a snowflake, because I've fallen for you.",
            "Is your name Google? Because you have everything I've been searching for.",
            "I'm not usually this forward, but you are the most beautiful person I have ever seen.",
            "Do you have a map? I keep getting lost in your eyes.",
            "I'm sorry, I seem to have lost my phone number. Can I have yours?",
            "Your hand looks heavy. Let me hold it for you. üòâ"
        ];
        let cheesyLineIndex = 0;
        let typingTimeout;
        
        // --- Code Unlock Logic ---
        function checkCode() {
            const enteredCode = document.getElementById('secretCode').value.toUpperCase().trim();
            const lockScreen = document.getElementById('lockScreen');
            const surpriseContent = document.getElementById('surpriseContent');
            const errorMsg = document.getElementById('errorMsg');
            const bdaySong = document.getElementById('bdaySong');

            if (enteredCode === SECRET_CODE) {
                lockScreen.style.display = 'none';
                surpriseContent.classList.remove('hidden');
                
                bdaySong.play().catch(error => { console.log("Audio playback failed:", error); });
                
                showNextStep(1);
            } else {
                errorMsg.textContent = "‚ùå Incorrect Key. Please check the code and try again!";
                setTimeout(() => { errorMsg.textContent = ''; }, 3000); 
            }
        }
        
        // --- Step-by-Step Logic ---
        let currentStep = 0;
        
        function showNextStep(stepNumber) {
            if (currentStep > 0) {
                const prevElement = document.getElementById('step' + currentStep);
                if(prevElement) {
                    prevElement.classList.remove('visible');
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        prevElement.classList.add('hidden');
                    }, 500); 
                }
            }

            currentStep = stepNumber;
            const nextElement = document.getElementById('step' + currentStep);
            
            if (nextElement) {
                nextElement.classList.remove('hidden'); 
                setTimeout(() => {
                    nextElement.classList.add('visible');
                    nextElement.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });

                    if (currentStep === 2) {
                        startTypewriter(); 
                    } else if (currentStep === 5) {
                        cheesyLineIndex = 0; 
                        typeNextCheesyLine();
                    }
                }, 50); 
            }
        }

        // --- Back to Lock Screen Logic ---
        function backToLockScreen() {
            const lockScreen = document.getElementById('lockScreen');
            const surpriseContent = document.getElementById('surpriseContent');
            const bdaySong = document.getElementById('bdaySong');
            
            // 1. Stop Audio
            bdaySong.pause();
            bdaySong.currentTime = 0;

            // 2. Hide Content
            surpriseContent.classList.add('hidden');
            
            // 3. Reset visible sections (ensure current one is hidden)
            for (let i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
                const stepElement = document.getElementById('step' + i);
                if (stepElement) {
                    stepElement.classList.remove('visible');
                    stepElement.classList.add('hidden');
                }
            }
            
            // 4. Show Lock Screen and scroll to top
            lockScreen.style.display = 'flex';
            window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
            
            // 5. Clear code input
            document.getElementById('secretCode').value = '';
            
            currentStep = 0;
        }


        // --- Typewriter Effect Logic for Letter ---
        const messageText_full = `
        Dear Madam Ji,

        whenever you go, your heart is pure gold, and your spirit is absolutely infectious.

       Thank you for being the wonderful, amazing, absolutely fantastic person that you are. The world is so much brighter because you're in it.

        Happy Birthday, beautiful soul! üéÇ‚ú®

        With all my love and warmest wishes,
        Forever Yours
        `;
        let charIndex = 0;
        
        function startTypewriter() {
            const typewriterElement = document.getElementById('typewriterText');
            const nextButton = document.getElementById('nextButton2');
            const readAgainBtn = document.getElementById('readAgainBtn');
            const letterCard = document.getElementById('letterCard');

            // Clear previous animation states
            clearTimeout(typingTimeout);
            letterCard.classList.remove('typing-done');
            typewriterElement.textContent = '';
            charIndex = 0;
            nextButton.classList.add('hidden');
            readAgainBtn.classList.add('hidden');

            function type() {
                if (charIndex < messageText_full.length) {
                    if (messageText_full.charAt(charIndex) === '\n') {
                         typewriterElement.innerHTML += '<br>';
                    } else {
                         typewriterElement.textContent += messageText_full.charAt(charIndex);
                    }
                    
                    charIndex++;
                    typingTimeout = setTimeout(type, typeSpeed);
                } else {
                    letterCard.classList.add('typing-done'); // Stop blinking cursor
                    nextButton.classList.remove('hidden');
                    readAgainBtn.classList.remove('hidden');
                }
            }
            type();
        }
        
        function readMessageAgain() {
             startTypewriter();
        }

        // --- Cheesy Lines Typing Logic (FIXED) ---
        function typeNextCheesyLine() {
            const outputElement = document.getElementById('cheesyLinesOutput');
            const tapNextElement = document.getElementById('tapToSeeNext');
            const cheesyContainer = document.querySelector('.cheesy-container');
            
            clearTimeout(typingTimeout);
            cheesyContainer.classList.remove('typing-done');
            
            if (cheesyLineIndex < CHEESY_LINES.length) {
                const line = CHEESY_LINES[cheesyLineIndex];
                outputElement.textContent = ''; // Clear previous text
                tapNextElement.textContent = ''; // Clear tap prompt
                
                let i = 0;
                function typeChar() {
                    if (i < line.length) {
                        outputElement.textContent += line.charAt(i);
                        i++;
                        typingTimeout = setTimeout(typeChar, CHEESY_TYPE_SPEED); 
                    } else {
                        // Typing is finished for this line
                        cheesyContainer.classList.add('typing-done');
                        tapNextElement.textContent = "Tap to see the next beautiful line...";
                        cheesyLineIndex++;
                    }
                }
                typeChar();
            } else {
                // All lines displayed
                outputElement.textContent = "That's all the lines for now! Hope they made you smile! üòä";
                cheesyContainer.classList.add('typing-done');
                tapNextElement.textContent = "Scroll up for more surprises or down for the final message!";
                cheesyLineIndex = 0; // Reset for potential re-viewing
            }
        }

        // --- Confetti/Cake Cutting Logic ---
        document.getElementById('cutCakeBtn').addEventListener('click', function() {
             confetti({
                particleCount: 300,
                spread: 150,
                origin: { y: 0.6 },
                startVelocity: 60,
                ticks: 400,
                colors: ['#ff007f', '#8a2be2', '#ffff00', '#ffffff', '#ff479a'] 
            });

            this.textContent = "üéâ CELEBRATION MODE ON! üéâ";
            this.style.backgroundColor = '#8a2be2';
            this.disabled = true;
            
            document.getElementById('nextButton3').classList.remove('hidden');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
